description: Wild In The Woods:  What would you do if you suddenly came across two heavy hung studs carrying on in the wild?  If you're anything like our friend you'd join them - he does and you join in too, with a three-way exercise in sex in the great outdoors.  These guys are imaginitive, but don't try to out guess them.  They still have a few surprises for you!
title: Fist Full, Scene #01
